---
import "../styles/global.css"
---
<div>
    <h1>Your One Stop Solution for All Things Tools & Hardware</h1>
    <p>Whitfield hardware offers a wide selection of professional-grade tools, hardware, and materials for home
        improvement,
        construction, maintenance, and more. Shop our inventory today!</p>
    <div class="columns-2">
        <div class="flex-item">
            <h2>Large Inventory</h2>
            <img width="375px" height="200px" src="/images/hero-inventory.png" alt="inventory">
            <p>We stock thousands of products from all the top brands. Find exactly what you need for any job, big or
                small. Our huge warehouse means we always have items in stock and ready to ship.</p>
            <a href="/inventory">Shop Inventory >></a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-item">
            <h2>Everyday Low Prices</h2>
            <img width="375px" height="200px" src="/images/hero-deals.png" alt="deals">
            <p>As a leading hardware supplier, we're able to offer exceptional prices across our entire product catalog.
                Take advantage of our wholesale discounts today.</p>
            <a href="/deals">See Deals >></a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    div {
        color: white;
        background-color: #e36910;
    }

    .top {
        padding: 200px 0;
    }

    .flex-container {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 20px;
    }

    .flex-item {
        flex: 1 1 45%;
    }

    .flex-item h2 {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        text-align: center;
    }
</style>